                <head>No. 140.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lowell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1884-02-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 19, 1884</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Formal offer Alert from Government came this morning.</p>
                <p>Admiralty find many things wanting; from press of work can do nothing; but Greens
                    promise her in three weeks, with most of equipment.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LOWELL,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Minister.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
